{"title":"什么是模型设计师？","slug":"bfdqvkhzgtd1nigv","summary":"本文主要探讨了模型设计师作为新兴角色在人工智能设计领域的重要性，以及设计师如何通过与工程师紧密合作，深入研究和塑造 AI 模型，以解决用户体验中的问题，如幻觉、隐私和偏见等。 观点 设计师应该超越界面设计，深入研究和塑造 AI 模型，以创造更用户友好且负责任的未来 。 AI 模型","category":"PART3️⃣ 产品设计师AI能力矩阵","tags":["PART3️⃣ 产品设计师AI能力矩阵"],"featured":false,"order":51,"level":1,"updatedAt":"2025-08-03","wordCount":1900,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/bfdqvkhzgtd1nigv","html":"<card type=\"block\" name=\"bookmarklink\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22card%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fuxdesign.cc%2Fthe-rise-of-the-model-designer-cef429d9c134%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fuxdesign.cc%2Fthe-rise-of-the-model-designer-cef429d9c134%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QHYqo%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><blockquote data-lake-id=\"u6812c486\" id=\"u6812c486\" class=\"lake-alert lake-alert-info\"><p data-lake-id=\"u99f36d7d\" id=\"u99f36d7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue608c654\" id=\"ue608c654\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">本文主要探讨了模型设计师作为新兴角色在人工智能设计领域的重要性，以及设计师如何通过与工程师紧密合作，深入研究和塑造 AI 模型，以解决用户体验中的问题，如幻觉、隐私和偏见等。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"2db04b6a\" id=\"2db04b6a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb7bb411\" id=\"ucb7bb411\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-headings)\">观点</span></h1><ul list=\"ucc2241d4\"><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"u74b93772\" id=\"u74b93772\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubfeb896e\" id=\"ubfeb896e\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70); background-color: #FBDE28\">设计师应该超越界面设计，深入研究和塑造 AI 模型，以创造更用户友好且负责任的未来</span><span data-lake-id=\"uffbcd168\" id=\"uffbcd168\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"uc449c0a6\" id=\"uc449c0a6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u211f6fc0\" id=\"u211f6fc0\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">AI 模型不仅是工具，也是需要塑造的原材料，设计师需要与工程师紧密合作，以解决模型构建中的问题。</span><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-links)\"><u><strong><sup><span data-lake-id=\"ue0469953\" id=\"ue0469953\">​</span></sup></strong></u></span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"uff121cdf\" id=\"uff121cdf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1da836a7\" id=\"u1da836a7\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">模型设计师作为新角色的出现，涉及到与工程师的紧密合作，以及对 AI 模型开发的深入理解。</span><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-links)\"><u><strong><sup><span data-lake-id=\"u63ef17b2\" id=\"u63ef17b2\">​</span></sup></strong></u></span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"ub46dfebd\" id=\"ub46dfebd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2b283b2a\" id=\"u2b283b2a\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">模型设计师可以通过创新的方法，如制作系统级提示、协作塑造数据集等，来提升产品的用户体验。</span><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-links)\"><u><strong><sup><span data-lake-id=\"ue42a7c25\" id=\"ue42a7c25\">​</span></sup></strong></u></span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"uccabad2e\" id=\"uccabad2e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8faa986\" id=\"ub8faa986\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">设计师需要重新定义角色，以适应 AI 的发展，这包括</span><span data-lake-id=\"u4356d69c\" id=\"u4356d69c\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70); background-color: #FBDE28\">内容设计师、研究人员和对话设计师</span><span data-lake-id=\"uf2cd863f\" id=\"uf2cd863f\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">等角色的职责调整。</span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"u359c3d9a\" id=\"u359c3d9a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u04905314\" id=\"u04905314\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">设计师应该具备技术知识、优秀的写作能力，以及对整个用户体验的深刻理解，以成为模型设计师。</span><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-links)\"><u><strong><sup><span data-lake-id=\"u8cb96f73\" id=\"u8cb96f73\">​</span></sup></strong></u></span></li><li fid=\"u9b5aa56e\" data-lake-id=\"ub97b49ee\" id=\"ub97b49ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf6f4bb97\" id=\"uf6f4bb97\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 70)\">设计师们应该保持好奇心，不断学习和适应 AI 模型设计的新时代。</span></li></ul></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"u00975975\" id=\"u00975975\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u716893da\" id=\"u716893da\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733280026915-59bb323c-36a3-4e10-9806-05b6299fe24d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u95e339ee-7da3-4997-bb21-1effd4b45be%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4f76ef0d-deea-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A800%2C%22height%22%3A314%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A150160%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A628%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22SHAPE%20MODELS%20DESIGN%20INTERACTIONS%20USE%20PRODUCTS%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A1279%2C%22y%22%3A507%2C%22width%22%3A211%2C%22height%22%3A47%2C%22text%22%3A%22SHAPE%20MODELS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A741%2C%22y%22%3A511%2C%22width%22%3A300%2C%22height%22%3A46%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%20INTERACTIONS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A154%2C%22y%22%3A510%2C%22width%22%3A203%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22USE%20PRODUCTS%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f1f1f1%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u53955cda%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uab0b20cb\" id=\"uab0b20cb\" style=\"text-align: center\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u233f739d\" id=\"u233f739d\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">Karthik Srinivas 的“使用产品”插图 — Blush.design</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf871876b\" id=\"uf871876b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8f544349\" id=\"u8f544349\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">在过去的一年里，随着人工智能模型的普及，设计师们忙于构思新产品和改进现有产品。我们一直专注于</span><span data-lake-id=\"u22f7f6d1\" id=\"u22f7f6d1\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">研究人们如何与这些模型互动</span><span data-lake-id=\"u08f83d73\" id=\"u08f83d73\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">，以新颖、创新的方式解决问题。这就像一场设计淘金热，充满了兴奋和探索。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"udeeffbd8\" id=\"udeeffbd8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u483029a5\" id=\"u483029a5\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">然而，我们缺少了一个关键部分：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u0a2d118c\" id=\"u0a2d118c\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107); background-color: #FBDE28\">我们主要关注界面（人们如何使用模型），而没有深入研究核心（模型本身）。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u5c287ed7\" id=\"u5c287ed7\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">这个核心是真正用户友好且负责任的未来的关键部分。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6f9db880\" id=\"u6f9db880\"><a href=\"http://cassie%20kozyrkov/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u624bfb6c\" id=\"u624bfb6c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf0a400ad\" id=\"uf0a400ad\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">目前，我们将这些 AI 模型视为工具，但正如Cassie Kozyrkov 解释的</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u8cb3e185\" id=\"u8cb3e185\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">那样，这些模型不仅仅是工具，它们也是原材料。它们就像需要塑造的粘土，特别是因为</span><span data-lake-id=\"u9c6c84a8\" id=\"u9c6c84a8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">现在很多用户体验都嵌入在模型本身中</span><span data-lake-id=\"u6d02a46e\" id=\"u6d02a46e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u64a7e2ec\" id=\"u64a7e2ec\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hallucination_(artificial_intelligence)\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u246fcf9e\" id=\"u246fcf9e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9b3b07b0\" id=\"u9b3b07b0\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">幻觉</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"ue8df3249\" id=\"ue8df3249\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">、</span><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/legal/legalindustry/privacy-paradox-with-ai-2023-10-31/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ueb30074d\" id=\"ueb30074d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u84a3c695\" id=\"u84a3c695\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">隐私</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u0b750b5d\" id=\"u0b750b5d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">和</span><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2023/feb/08/biased-ai-algorithms-racy-women-bodies#:~:text=Two%20Guardian%20journalists%20used%20the,everyday%20situations%20as%20sexually%20suggestive.\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u1e277a7d\" id=\"u1e277a7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u13ec0e69\" id=\"u13ec0e69\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">偏见</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"ue9fc3769\" id=\"ue9fc3769\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">等问题</span><span data-lake-id=\"u7a104004\" id=\"u7a104004\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">不仅仅是用户在与 AI 模型交互时遇到的问题。这些问题与模型的构建方式息息相关。为了有效解决这些问题，我们需要与工程团队进行比目前更紧密的合作。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9ab59803\" id=\"u9ab59803\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58172dd7\" id=\"u58172dd7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">为了应对这一切，一个新的设计角色正在出现，我称之为</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u43e4dc79\" id=\"u43e4dc79\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">“模型设计师”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc165830f\" id=\"uc165830f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。这些专家与专注于用户与产品之间交互的传统用户体验团队一起工作。与他们不同的是，</span><span data-lake-id=\"u55f4133c\" id=\"u55f4133c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">模型设计师研究得更深入，直接与开发人工智能模型的工程师合作</span><span data-lake-id=\"u90582e64\" id=\"u90582e64\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc3f145e1\" id=\"uc3f145e1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubcd6103e\" id=\"ubcd6103e\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">对于小型设计团队，模型设计师的角色可能是现有团队成员的额外责任。这意味着学习新技能并承担与塑造 AI 模型相关的新任务。对于拥有更成熟设计实践的大型公司，模型设计师可能是专门的合作者，或是一个整体用户体验团队。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u014c274d\" id=\"u014c274d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4df614ea\" id=\"u4df614ea\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">专家可以将他们在 AI 模型开发方面的垂直专业知识带入设计流程，与界面设计师合作打造更好的产品</span><span data-lake-id=\"u6fd6fa47\" id=\"u6fd6fa47\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。他们的综合技能涵盖了整个工作流程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5619056\" id=\"uc5619056\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4ca0f84a\" id=\"u4ca0f84a\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">举几个例子：</span></p><ul list=\"u5694b71d\"><li fid=\"u6c0c9305\" data-lake-id=\"u8841b40c\" id=\"u8841b40c\"><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/docs/generative-ai/learn/introduction-prompt-design#:~:text=Prompt%20design%20is%20the%20process,responses%20from%20a%20language%20model.\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u66a72350\" id=\"u66a72350\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueb934ff6\" id=\"ueb934ff6\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">提示</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u20a041ab\" id=\"u20a041ab\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">非常痛苦，即使</span><a href=\"https://www.aiforeducation.io/ai-resources/the-five-s-model\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u028f68a7\" id=\"u028f68a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab8ac521\" id=\"uab8ac521\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">使用框架</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u967753b5\" id=\"u967753b5\" style=\"color: currentcolor; background-color: rgb(243, 240, 239)\">作为指导，它需要用户承担很大的认知负荷。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"u5694b71d\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u6c0c9305\" data-lake-id=\"u367f1f1f\" id=\"u367f1f1f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u682f48d7\" id=\"u682f48d7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">UX 设计师可以通过创建上下文建议提示来缓解这种情况。</span></li><li fid=\"u6c0c9305\" data-lake-id=\"u639d63f5\" id=\"u639d63f5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u96a6ab6e\" id=\"u96a6ab6e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">模型设计师可以制作系统级提示，如序言，甚至可以更深入地协作塑造数据集以进行微调。有关背景，请参阅</span><a href=\"https://txt.cohere.com/exploring-chat-rag/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ufd21fbb9\" id=\"ufd21fbb9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u907dcb29\" id=\"u907dcb29\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Cohere 博客</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u6f52b710\" id=\"u6f52b710\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">：</span><em><span data-lake-id=\"u020859ab\" id=\"u020859ab\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">序言包含指令，可帮助引导聊天机器人的响应针对特定特征，例如角色、风格或格式*，从而使用户无需编写冗长的文本。</span></em></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u6db90f64\" id=\"u6db90f64\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733280040469-38d9ce5c-94f4-41da-a7ab-03d28ea9e5e8.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub3d6dec6-b421-4cd5-a372-91c2e85a85b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4f76ef0d-deea-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A641%2C%22height%22%3A270%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A89860%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1282%2C%22originHeight%22%3A540%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22PREAMBLE%20PROMPT%20USER'S%20CONTENT%20ASK%20A%20QUESTION%20SUGGESTION%20CHIPS%20INTERNAL%20PROMPTS%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A888%2C%22y%22%3A143%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22PREAMBLE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A664%2C%22y%22%3A228%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROMPT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A871%2C%22y%22%3A244%2C%22width%22%3A170%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22USER'S%20CONTENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A98%2C%22y%22%3A332%2C%22width%22%3A125%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22ASK%20A%20QUESTION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A448%2C%22width%22%3A308%2C%22height%22%3A59%2C%22text%22%3A%22SUGGESTION%20CHIPS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A802%2C%22y%22%3A451%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A40%2C%22text%22%3A%22INTERNAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A956%2C%22y%22%3A452%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A55%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROMPTS%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f3f3%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0eb76aec%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5f2fdd9d\" id=\"u5f2fdd9d\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"u798fa588\" id=\"u798fa588\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">可见的建议与不可见的预建提示</span></p><ul list=\"ub9b4e809\"><li fid=\"ub3824c34\" data-lake-id=\"ue89bab9e\" id=\"ue89bab9e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufb8caf86\" id=\"ufb8caf86\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">为了解决</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3d313138\" id=\"u3d313138\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">潜在的偏见</span></strong></li></ul><ul list=\"ub9b4e809\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"ub3824c34\" data-lake-id=\"u7d77462d\" id=\"u7d77462d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueb706c64\" id=\"ueb706c64\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">用户体验设计者可以通过在界面中加入</span><a href=\"https://www.feisworld.com/blog/disclaimer-templates-for-ai-generated-content\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u4916b0dc\" id=\"u4916b0dc\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubc323cdb\" id=\"ubc323cdb\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">免责声明</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u734c6f85\" id=\"u734c6f85\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">来补充这些努力，以最大限度地减少偏见反应造成的潜在危害。</span></li><li fid=\"ub3824c34\" data-lake-id=\"ud2e8453c\" id=\"ud2e8453c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uac2f3d9b\" id=\"uac2f3d9b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">模型设计者可以与工程师合作实施策略，例如在特定语境中屏蔽特定词语。</span></li></ul><ul list=\"ub9b4e809\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"ub3824c34\" data-lake-id=\"uefa74743\" id=\"uefa74743\"><a href=\"https://www.fastcompany.com/91006321/how-ai-companies-are-trying-to-solve-the-llm-hallucination-problem\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u85dab579\" id=\"u85dab579\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf5a03f1e\" id=\"uf5a03f1e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">通过将模型接地，可以最大限度地减少幻觉</span></a></li></ul><ul list=\"ub9b4e809\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"ub3824c34\" data-lake-id=\"u4f3c293b\" id=\"u4f3c293b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fda3909\" id=\"u7fda3909\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">UX 和模型设计师可以与工程团队一起合作开发强大的反馈周期。按照</span><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/research\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u3acbeff2\" id=\"u3acbeff2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua789d793\" id=\"ua789d793\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">Anthropic 的方法</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u130ca689\" id=\"u130ca689\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">，模型设计师还可以创建一组</span><span data-lake-id=\"u41e02b0d\" id=\"u41e02b0d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">对抗训练的原则</span><span data-lake-id=\"u146abe74\" id=\"u146abe74\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">（或</span><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/index/collective-constitutional-ai-aligning-a-language-model-with-public-input\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ud01e0242\" id=\"ud01e0242\"><span data-lake-id=\"u90d00a23\" id=\"u90d00a23\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">宪法</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"ua7d78ab8\" id=\"ua7d78ab8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">），其中对抗模型将挑战原始模型的输出。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u67ded61d\" id=\"u67ded61d\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733280049408-98e10c67-97c1-467d-9a82-8e65bcc9de43.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9bb58873-1264-4e2b-82c8-0b75c3a783a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4f76ef0d-deea-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A800%2C%22height%22%3A470%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A254970%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A939%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22RLHF*(ALIGNMENT)%20REINFORCE%20LEARNING%20HUMAN%20FEEDBACK%20COMPANY%20DATA%20CONTEXF%20TRAIN%20ON%20TOP%20OF%20THE%20PRE-TRAINED%20MODEL%20USER%20INFERACTS%20FOUNDATIONAL%20MODEL%20WIFH%20MODEL%20TRAINING%20THE%20MODEL%20DATA%20BY%20USER%20PATA%20MODEL%20DESIGNER%20UX%20DESIGNER%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A1113%2C%22y%22%3A72%2C%22width%22%3A196%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22RLHF*(ALIGNMENT)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1025%2C%22y%22%3A102%2C%22width%22%3A374%2C%22height%22%3A37%2C%22text%22%3A%22REINFORCE%20LEARNING%20HUMAN%20FEEDBACK%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A667%2C%22y%22%3A146%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMPANY%20DATA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A693%2C%22y%22%3A180%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONTEXF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A519%2C%22y%22%3A220%2C%22width%22%3A165%2C%22height%22%3A35%2C%22text%22%3A%22TRAIN%20ON%20TOP%20OF%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A514%2C%22y%22%3A253%2C%22width%22%3A175%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22THE%20PRE-TRAINED%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A572%2C%22y%22%3A291%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1093%2C%22y%22%3A321%2C%22width%22%3A149%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22USER%20INFERACTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A168%2C%22y%22%3A329%2C%22width%22%3A176%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOUNDATIONAL%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1116%2C%22y%22%3A354%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22WIFH%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A48%2C%22y%22%3A601%2C%22width%22%3A189%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22TRAINING%20THE%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1075%2C%22y%22%3A743%2C%22width%22%3A146%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22DATA%20BY%20USER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A249%2C%22y%22%3A772%2C%22width%22%3A47%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22PATA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A451%2C%22y%22%3A852%2C%22width%22%3A153%2C%22height%22%3A38%2C%22text%22%3A%22MODEL%20DESIGNER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1153%2C%22y%22%3A854%2C%22width%22%3A124%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22UX%20DESIGNER%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcf5f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6906c8a2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u69e62d25\" id=\"u69e62d25\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb90f890\" id=\"ucb90f890\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">模型设计者主要关注“对齐”部分</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0f50002e\" id=\"u0f50002e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0d029067\" id=\"u0d029067\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">以新的方式合作也意味着新的协作产物，一种专注于</span><span data-lake-id=\"u70e608a2\" id=\"u70e608a2\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">开放式用例</span><span data-lake-id=\"u92c1884d\" id=\"u92c1884d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">的</span><a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/service-blueprints-definition/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u86c2cafe\" id=\"u86c2cafe\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua783973c\" id=\"ua783973c\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">服务设计蓝图。PAIR</span></a><a href=\"https://pair.withgoogle.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ue740e484\" id=\"ue740e484\"><span data-lake-id=\"u49cd4952\" id=\"u49cd4952\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">（谷歌的 People + AI 研究）</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u14ce402f\" id=\"u14ce402f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">正在发布一些围绕使用 AI 模型（而不仅仅是任务）时的交互设计策略的</span><a href=\"https://medium.com/people-ai-research/interaction-design-policies-design-for-the-opportunity-not-just-the-task-239e7f294b29\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"ud9936acf\" id=\"ud9936acf\"><span data-lake-id=\"uca03772f\" id=\"uca03772f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">协作框架。</span></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf2282b7d\" id=\"uf2282b7d\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u461d9f70\" id=\"u461d9f70\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">除了模型设计师如何协作的例子之外，随着人工智能的发展，</span></em><a href=\"https://hbr.org/2023/12/genai-will-change-how-we-design-jobs-heres-how\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"uda87c430\" id=\"uda87c430\"><em><span data-lake-id=\"u50c81f9f\" id=\"u50c81f9f\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">重新定义角色的需求越来越大</span></em></a><em><span data-lake-id=\"ubccdecbf\" id=\"ubccdecbf\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。公司正在重组设计团队，在许多情况下，角色职责并不明确。对于大多数不从事人工智能项目的团队来说，人们甚至不知道新角色的出现。</span></em></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf480b6f6\" id=\"uf480b6f6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uaf69dd20\" id=\"uaf69dd20\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">内容设计师</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2d8a344b\" id=\"u2d8a344b\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">现在正在制定详细的训练模型指南，承担大部分工作，因为</span><span data-lake-id=\"u025bf1cc\" id=\"u025bf1cc\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: #FBDE28\">语言是大多数人工智能模型的货币</span><span data-lake-id=\"u53d9b79d\" id=\"u53d9b79d\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。他们的日常工作与传统的内容设计师大不相同，他们从事交互方面的工作，但他们的头衔是一样的。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u154720b3\" id=\"u154720b3\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8abdf00e\" id=\"u8abdf00e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">研究人员</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub54c8603\" id=\"ub54c8603\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">正在设想数据集如何反映用户意图，并将其与他们开发的角色相匹配。致力于人工智能助手的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u940fac18\" id=\"u940fac18\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">对话设计师</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5d609f00\" id=\"u5d609f00\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">正在打破传统的决策树，并创建一系列提示。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaf91d0c4\" id=\"uaf91d0c4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u135c3105\" id=\"u135c3105\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">UX 设计师</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud64c2cb8\" id=\"ud64c2cb8\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">正在转向战略层面，他们可以协调模型的塑造和用户端所需的交互。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub622fc0b\" id=\"ub622fc0b\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1733280057331-c853a57a-57da-4c52-8ca5-f21b6b15d93a.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u4c063c93-d6ea-447b-868e-03a42b33c3d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4f76ef0d-deea-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A365%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A223302%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A730%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22N%20CHARGE%20OF%20MODEL%20ENG%20ENG%20DATA%20SCIENTIST%20%2FENG%20PRODUCT%20DESIGN%20PRODUCT%20DESIGN%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A1197%2C%22y%22%3A58%2C%22width%22%3A143%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22N%20CHARGE%20OF%20MODEL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A314%2C%22y%22%3A253%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22ENG%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A896%2C%22y%22%3A257%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22ENG%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1140%2C%22y%22%3A262%2C%22width%22%3A167%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22DATA%20SCIENTIST%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1189%2C%22y%22%3A300%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22%2FENG%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A115%2C%22y%22%3A500%2C%22width%22%3A100%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRODUCT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A457%2C%22y%22%3A515%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A845%2C%22y%22%3A525%2C%22width%22%3A100%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRODUCT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1178%2C%22y%22%3A531%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e2e8e4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1e68cb5e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5f890967\" id=\"u5f890967\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubc9153a9\" id=\"ubc9153a9\" style=\"color: rgb(107, 107, 107)\">将 LLM 工程师团队纳入日常协作</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9b2d476c\" id=\"u9b2d476c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee9fb7eb\" id=\"uee9fb7eb\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">模型设计师具备上述所有素质；有很多切入点，也有很多技能需要掌握。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u590e568e\" id=\"u590e568e\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">它需要结合技术知识、出色的写作能力以及对端到端用户体验的深刻理解</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub0b85df4\" id=\"ub0b85df4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。除了特定角色之外，</span><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/ux-needs-sense-urgency-ai-jakob-nielsen/\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u3499749d\" id=\"u3499749d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4a6e3fd5\" id=\"u4a6e3fd5\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">来自各个背景的设计师都应该了解模型的工作原理</span></a><span data-lake-id=\"u47db6ad4\" id=\"u47db6ad4\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">。永远保持好奇心从未像现在这样重要。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0dec74e1\" id=\"u0dec74e1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufdbf75b7\" id=\"ufdbf75b7\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36)\">对于我们的工艺来说这是一个激动人心的时刻。</span></p>"}
